turnkey-punbb-15.0 (1) turnkey; urgency=low

  * Patched to be compatible with PHP7 (via 3rd party community patches - see
    https://punbb.info/t-1010.html (Russian).
    [ Jeremy Davis ]

  * Redirect IP to domain (set at firstboot) and all traffic to https.
    [ Jeremy Davis ]

  * Install Adminer directly from stretch/main repo

  * Provide "adminer" root-like user for Adminer MySQL access

  * Replace MySQL with MariaDB (drop-in MySQL replacement)

  * Updated version of mysqltuner script

  * Includes PHP7.0 (installed from Debian repos)

  * Updated PHP default settings

  * Remove phpsh (no longer maintained)

  * Note: Please refer to turnkey-core's changelog for changes common to all
    appliances. Here we only describe changes specific to this appliance.

